metadata.name: I Can't Help It
metadata.description:
I Can't Help It

Written, recorded, & mixed by Miles Ryan Harris (@milesryanharris)

Mastered by DJ Twinny Twin (@djtwinnytwin)

Artwork by Grafik (@grxfk)

Lyrics:

I treat the beat like a b*tch  
I can tell if it’s me off the rip  
Soon as I seen you I said sh*t  
Ain’t gotta look no further baby that’s it

2 phone calls 3 DMs  
Woke up at like 3 pm  
My tempo was a medium  
Now it’s more like EDM

I rave about you  
Got a notebook that deserve a page about you  
A ring to give you  
With a diamond as cold as my days without you

I'm a hopeless  
Romantic going manic with the focus  
Had 3 tabs open when I wrote this 
Might let Yung Pueblo quote this  
You the dark in the night where ghost is  
You the light that I need when I smoke this  
Always take me to high places  
But dope is, deadly in high doses

I do what I want 
I like what I like 
I can’t help it

I love what I love  
That pussy like drugs  
I can’t help it

Want you to myself  
I’m too selfish...
